overview: Carl Gustav Jung interviewed on the subject of 'Sigmund Freud': how Jung met him, how he was influenced by him and where he disagreed with him. Jung talks about word association, Freudian slips, the unconscious, the Oedipus complex, the ego, archetypes, falling in love and more.

production_companies.name: Pennsylvania State University Psychological Cinema Register

title: Jung Speaks of Freud
